data.title: Future of Drupal: 7, 8 or just Drupal 9? testtt
data.summary: With Drupal’s commitment to reinventing itself to enable ambitious digital experiences, the community is getting ready for the launch of Drupal 9, and end-of-life for Drupal 7 and Drupal 8.

data.title: Should Your Enterprise Go For a Headless Commerce Architecture?
data.summary: E-commerce enterprises looking to deliver seamless user experiences, often wonder how to do so. Is there a way that does not require them to invent their own IoT device or build back-end solutions from scratch?
